title: Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.

title: Earth
subTitle: The disaster of Indian/Pakistani partition seen through the eyes of a child - Lenny, an eight-year-old crippled girl - from Lahore, the Punjabi city that saw some of the bloodiest pogroms. The experiences, hopes and fears of this young girl provide an intense portrait of the period.

title: The Great Indian Butterfly

title: Tantra
subTitle: Rekha, a timid woman, has the ability to perceive spirits. When she encounters a malevolent black magic practitioner, she is drawn into unravelling dark occult mysteries, putting her life at risk.

title: Theeran

title: Kali Kitaab

title: Vijay Raghavan

title: Gangs of Godavari

title: Devara: Part 1

title: Alluri
